<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Lei Hansie Dawl !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lei hansie dawl nachung ahin,
 Gitloh lummei pi hung zingin;
 Ka Lal mel deihum a lieh zo,
 Khuo hung vak ding ngakin:

[V2]
 Thim nuoiah ka um ie,
 Zingkhuo'n hung vak kitin;
 Thim nuoiah kapin ka vai.
 Pielgal ni'n hun salhvakin. (2) D S.

[V3]
 2. Buoina tuipi na chung ahin,
 Galili tui kinawk bangin;
 Dogal tuibang hung lien mahleh.
 Huih leh guohpi nuoiah

[V4]
 Lungkham leh gim um in.
 Ei umvel mah leu le;
 Lawng nunglam ah Lal Isu ,
 Ei panpih din A nai zing. (2) D S.

[V5]
 3. Zan thim nuoia khawvak ngakte,
 Tuchan hinle a thawn ngei puou;
 Kei le ka Lal Isu ngakin.
 A thutiema dingin;

[V6]
 Lal David thaumei vak,
 Ka kalsuonna lampi;
 Ka lu ei liehkhuh dingin,
 Lal thaumei a vak kit tai (2) D S.

[V7]
 4. Na sulnung hun zuiin Lalpa,
 Gimum khuombang ka dona cheng;
 Lungsietna thilpiek ahi ie,
 Zan thim I khel ta maw;

[V8]
 Khuo ahung vak kit tai,
 Tho un Zion chate;
 Gam lun ding na sem hitiu,
 Meipi zing a kithiel tai. (2) D S.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>160</hymn_number>
<author>Ngama</author>
</song>